00:01:16.955 --> 00:01:21.335
as your password will be sent to your phone and you will use it to log in 

00:01:21.535 --> 00:01:24.935
For your convenience you only have to save your address once

00:01:24.935 --> 00:01:29.435
you can also add a note for the restaurant like I did here

00:01:34.935 --> 00:01:39.535
1 minute later, the restaurant receives your order via the Eat.vn system

00:01:39.935 --> 00:01:44.135
Your order is printed with your address and all details

00:01:44.335 --> 00:01:46.935
including any note for the restaurant

00:01:46.935 --> 00:01:51.935
Now you can relax or continue working while waiting for the food 

00:01:52.035 --> 00:01:55.935
